%F A280207 Solution of tan(Pi/x) + sin(Pi/x)*cos(Pi/x) = 2*Pi/x. (No closed-form expression for x exists.)
%e A280207 3.18176012927017138762046804951303196421721246349351...
%t A280207 RealDigits[x /. FindRoot[Tan[Pi/x] + Sin[Pi/x] * Cos[Pi/x] == 2*Pi/x,{x, 3},WorkingPrecision->120]][[1]] (* _Amiram Eldar_, Jun 26 2023 *)
%o A280207 (PARI) solve(x=3,4, tan(Pi/x) + sin(Pi/x)*cos(Pi/x) - 2*Pi/x) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jul 23 2026
